```plantuml
@startuml chirgjin_track-my-events

actor User

participant "React App" as React
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "User Service" as UserService
participant "Tracking Service" as TrackingService
participant "Redis" as Redis
participant "PostgreSQL" as PostgreSQL

User -> React: Register/Login
React -> Gateway: POST /auth
Gateway -> UserService: POST /auth
UserService -> PostgreSQL: Validate User
PostgreSQL --> UserService: User Validated
UserService --> Gateway: Token
Gateway --> React: Token

User -> React: Integrate SDK
React -> React: Include tracking-sdk.js

User -> React: Event Trigger
React -> Gateway: POST /events
Gateway -> Redis: Publish Event

Redis -> TrackingService: Notify Event
TrackingService -> PostgreSQL: Store Event Data
PostgreSQL --> TrackingService: Data Stored

User -> React: View Dashboard
React -> Gateway: GET /dashboard
Gateway -> TrackingService: GET /events
TrackingService -> PostgreSQL: Retrieve Aggregated Data
PostgreSQL --> TrackingService: Data Retrieved
TrackingService --> Gateway: Aggregated Data
Gateway --> React: Dashboard Data

@enduml
```